			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Exhaust gases treated ; Soil ex-situ remediation ; Chemical Oxidation ; Secondary pollution disposal ; Treatment of wastewater and exhaust gas</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">处置后废气;土壤异位修复;化学氧化;二次污染防治;废水、废气处置</baseName>
			</name>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification>
					<common:class level="0">Unit processes</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Other Services</common:class>
					<common:class level="2">Repair and maintenance</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Secondary pollution prevention and control includes the installation and operation of waste gas and wastewater pollution prevention and control facilities, as well as the disposal of hazardous waste</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">二次污染防治包括废气及废水污染防治设施安装及运行、危险废物处置等过程</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
		<quantitativeReference type="Reference flow(s)">
			<functionalUnitOrOther xml:lang="en">Prevention and control of secondary pollution such as wastewater and exhaust gas generated during the ectopic chemical oxidation process of 59922m3 polluted soil.</functionalUnitOrOther>
			<referenceToReferenceFlow>4</referenceToReferenceFlow>
		</quantitativeReference>
		<time>
			<common:referenceYear>2024</common:referenceYear>
		</time>
		<geography>
			<locationOfOperationSupplyOrProduction location="ZB-SD-CN">
				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="en">The polluted site is located in Zibo City, Shandong Province, covering a total area of approximately 87800 m2.</descriptionOfRestrictions>
				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="zh">污染场地位于山东省淄博市，占地总面积约8.78万 m2。</descriptionOfRestrictions>
			</locationOfOperationSupplyOrProduction>
		</geography>
		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">Construction enclosed shed with a size of  80m x 32m x 9m. The total area of the enclosed shed  is 2560m2, and the thickness of the ground concrete is 20cm. The soil remediation process generates a total of 2481 m3 of wastewater, mainly from foundation pit wastewater and car washing pool wastewater. After being extracted and treated with chemical oxidation and coagulation sedimentation, it is discharged into the municipal sewage pipeline network. The chemical oxidation and coagulation agents are 2.5% sodium persulfate and 1 ‰ PAM+5% PAC, respectively; The restoration project generated a total of 4.19 tons of solid waste, all of which are hazardous waste, mainly activated carbon used for greenhouse exhaust gas adsorption and water treatment sludge, all of which are transported to qualified third-party units for disposal</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">土壤异位处置大棚建设，大棚尺寸80m×32m×9m，大棚总占地面积2560m2，地面混凝土浇筑厚度20cm；土壤修复过程共产生废水2481 m3，主要为基坑废水及洗车池废水，抽出后经化学氧化和混凝沉淀处理合格后排至市政污水管网，化学氧化及混凝药剂分别采用2.5%过硫酸钠和1‰PAM+5%PAC；修复工程共产生固废4.19吨，均为危险废物，主要为大棚尾气吸附所用活性炭以及水处理污泥，全部外运至第三方有资质单位处置</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The described industrial process is used for soil remediation at a polluted site through ex-situ chemical oxidation. The process involves constructing an enclosed shed to treat the polluted soil, managing wastewater and exhaust gases arising from the remediation, and ensuring secondary pollution control through the installation and operation of pollution prevention facilities. Additionally, the transportation and use of equipment, and disposal of hazardous waste such as used activated carbon and sludge, are integral parts of the process.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">此工业过程应用于一污染场地的土壤异位化学氧化修复。该过程包括修建封闭大棚处理受污染土壤，处理修复过程中产生的废水和废气，并通过建立和运行污染防治设施确保二次污染防治。此外，运输和使用设备以及处理诸如使用过的活性炭和污泥之类的危险废物，是该过程不可分割的一部分。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="71248eb7-7802-7c18-2d46-abb1caa9fd9a" uri="../sources/71248eb7-7802-7c18-2d46-abb1caa9fd9a.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">UlUnbUoQzobZIFxKHXWcNJq5nkf.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
