			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using this dataset for Life Cycle Assessment, it is vital to ensure that contributions to secondary pollution are assessed, including emissions from waste treatment facilities. Users should model the use phase behavior, considering the energy and material flows within the remediation process, the construction of the shed, and the subsequent disposal of hazardous waste. The applicability of this data is specific to polluted soil sites that involve similar soil remediation practices, and geographical relevance must be considered due to local environmental regulations impacting waste disposal and treatment.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用此数据集进行生命周期评估时，必须确保评估对二次污染的贡献，包括废物处理设施的排放。用户应当考虑修复过程中的能源与物料流、大棚建设以及随后的危险废物处置，对使用阶段的行为进行建模。这些数据的适用性具体针对涉及类似土壤修复实践的污染土壤场地，还必须考虑到地理相关性，因为当地环境法规会影响废物的处置和处理。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
